  ('medical-tech-moex-07908', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-106-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '糞便培養時，關於致病菌與最佳培養條件之配對，下列何者錯誤？', '["Shigella boydii–35℃，有氧培養箱", "Vibrio cholerae–35℃，有氧培養箱", "Campylobacter jejuni–42℃，微需氧培養箱", "Clostridium difficile–35℃，有氧培養箱"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e4a65d4b75e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1b85c79554b6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、藥師、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
