  ('medical-tech-moex-07913', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-106-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關Nocardia spp.之生長特性，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["可生長於Thayer-Martin agar", "可生長於buffered charcoal-yeast extract agar", "可在22～37℃生長", "大多數菌株生長快速，菌落平滑黏稠"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e4a65d4b75e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1b85c79554b6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、藥師、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-07914', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-106-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關臨床常見的Enterococcus spp.特性之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["porphyrin test呈陽性", "可在pH 9.6或10～45℃的環境中生長", "可耐受高濃度膽汁（bile）並水解esculin", "可水解L-pyrrolidonyl-β-naphthylamide"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e4a65d4b75e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1b85c79554b6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、藥師、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
